Either the concepts rely too much on action and banging, or they are too maudlin.
Richard Gere in &quot;The Hunting Party&quot; can&#39;t help either.
The good news first: Although the war criminals Karadzic and Mladic are still hiding in the mountains of the Balkans, it is precisely there, in the gloomy hinterland of the Bosnian war, that the actor Richard Gere has been found.
