It is almost always the case that when a star roams the world&#39;s trouble spots or minefields, the result is something like &quot;Rangoon&quot; with Patricia Arquette, &quot;Beyond All Limits&quot; with Angelina Jolie or &quot;Blood Diamonds&quot; with Leonardo DiCaprio.
